  "type": "EPCISDocument",
  "schemaVersion": "2.0",
  "creationDate": "2026-05-04T10:00:00.000Z",
  "_comment_architecture": [
    "Recyclability-grade declaration observation. Captures the Annex II design-for-recycling assessment result (grade, score, methodology) for a packaging lot as event-level sensor data. The lot is class-level (AI 01 + AI 10), so it travels in quantityList, not epcList.",
    "Architecture: the event references identifiers by URI — GTIN in epcList, GLN in readPoint/bizLocation, party GLN in source/destination. Model-, location-, and party-level master data is served by the GS1 Digital Link / Web Vocabulary resolver when those URIs are dereferenced; it is NOT embedded in the event.",
    "masterDataAvailableFor carries ONLY item/lot-level master data (e.g. countryOfOrigin, regulatoryInformation, harvestDate, EUDR plot geolocation). ilmd carries lot/instance data of the items this event creates. Observation extensions sit at event level.",
    "",
    "HTTP header: GS1-Extensions: oec=https://ref.openepcis.io/extensions/common/core/, euppwr=https://ref.openepcis.io/extensions/eu/ppwr/",
    "GS1 demo prefix 952 (7-digit GCP: 9521234)."
  ],
  "epcisBody": {
    "eventList": [
      {
        "type": "ObjectEvent",
        "eventID": "urn:uuid:5c2b4e90-1234-4abc-9876-1f2c3d4e5f64",
        "eventTime": "2026-05-04T09:30:00.000Z",
        "eventTimeZoneOffset": "+02:00",
        "action": "OBSERVE",
        "bizStep": "inspecting",
        "disposition": "active",
        "quantityList": [
          {
